00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.390
Sometimes, caffeine is a
bad self-medicating drug,

00:00:03.390 --> 00:00:04.750
causing all sorts of problems.

00:00:04.750 --> 00:00:07.305
But other times, it can be
really good for your brains.

00:00:13.546 --> 00:00:14.920
Hey y'all, Trace
here for D News,

